{
  "stem": "13874.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I compared it, being a history buff-- even at that young age, had read a lot of history, which included the crusades, the inquisition, all that stuff.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, what is the difference of it?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What's the difference between-- and to put it very frankly, between suffering ad majorem Dei glorium, which is the slogan of the Jesuits, or just for the hell of it?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I couldn't find any difference.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ad majorem Dei glorium.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That means for the greater glory of God.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That is the slogan of the Jesuits.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And just for the hell of it is what we went through.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I couldn't see much difference.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that is all the same God.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Lots of people came out of Dachau very religious.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think more of them-- and I was one of them-- without religion.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's where I really stopped believing, if I ever believed much.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I continued to go through the motions.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no way.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nothing like that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Actually, it's enough.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we were talking about food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was within the prison of Dachau, there was a compound with the barbed wire, with three barracks separated, which was reserved-- or it wasn't reserved-- which was the compound for the Jehovah's Witnesses.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were there because they refused to swear allegiance to the flag, or to the country or whatever else it is.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were kept there till they got up and swore allegiance.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They just didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were the only cohesive groups there who was a little bit-- who was concerned about their fellow prisoners.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And one of them was caught sharing his bread with somebody outside that particular compound.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So the commandant ruled, evidently we feed you too much.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Instead of half a loaf, you get only a third of a loaf.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
